cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with safe navigation of autonomous vehicles.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a data-driven mapping between features and driver behaviors.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the proposed features are extracted from vehicle trajectories.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a web-based user study to derive the mapping between features and driver behaviors.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper incorporates the algorithm into a vehicle navigation simulation system.
